<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFCarlisle2003">Carlisle, Rodney P (2003). <i>The Complete Idiot's Guide to Spies and Espionage</i>. Alpha Books. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0028644182" class="internal">ISBN 0-02-864418-2</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Complete+Idiot%27s+Guide+to+Spies+and+Espionage&amp;rft.aulast=Carlisle&amp;rft.aufirst=Rodney+P&amp;rft.au=Carlisle%2C+Rodney+P&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pub=Alpha+Books&amp;rft.isbn=0-02-864418-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Plausible_deniability"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> p. 213</li>
